reputation==========
Get a quick overview of someone's account at services like github, twitter etc.

Usage:
$ reputation <service> <account-name>

Where service can be one of:
- github
- twitter
- youtube

E.g. 
$ reputation github drnic

Full name:           Dr Nic Williams
Member since:        Jan 30, 2008 (376 days)
Public repositories: 71 (created: 48, forked: 23)
Followers:           354


Enjoy.


